tip.text: The side of bread was a lil too chewy. Sauce was great! It would be perfect if the side is as fluffy as the rest! Great job!
Services are good. But need more wide choices of food and beverage. Pancakes are too dense, need to improve on the texture. Caramel tasted like condense milk heated with sugar.

tip.text: They froth good fine milk, balanced latte with rich espresso base. Nice design, great spot for morning coffee time.
Reasonable price. Nice design and cosy environment. Coffee is okay, espresso is bit watery. Food looks great, will come back to have a try:)
They should notice that their decorations are blocking us from looking thru the menu on the wall. I ordered a Latte but what they served is a Capp. Food is good, staffs are nice.
